title: HORIZONS | Entry Seven: Just One Ship
itunes:title: HORIZONS | Entry Seven: Just One Ship
itunes:subtitle: Dismissed as primitive and ridiculed by her own allies, a single human ship is all that stands between those allies and oblivion.
description:
Dismissed as primitive and ridiculed by her own allies, a single human ship is all that stands between those allies and oblivion. Just One Ship is written by Alexander Bruce, performed by Aaron Cavette.
